third-party libraries needed to compile:
./3rd/glew-1.10.0
./3rd/freeglut-2.8.1
./3rd/glm
./3rd/audiere-1.9.4-win32
./3rd/FreeImage [3.15.4 version]

key controls:

F1 - draw FPS
ESC - exit game

[not working] v - draw HUD 
n - minimalize/maximalize
m - capture mouse

r - speed up
f - speed down

F9 - enable debug mode
debug mode options:

F8 - draw edges
F12 - draw debug info
k - draw collision edges
space - add asteroid
b - write map and vehicle position to file worldmap.txt






